# axslcc @AXSLCC_VERSION@

This package includes the axslcc shader cross-compiler and its runtime dependencies.

## Components

| Component | Version | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| axslcc    | @AXSLCC_VERSION@ | Shader cross-compiler |
| dxc       | @DXC_VERSION@ | DirectXShaderCompiler runtime library |
| fxc       | @DXC_FXC_VERSION@ | d3dcompiler_47.dll (Windows FXC runtime) |
| glslang   | 16.3.0 | GLSL/HLSL front-end |
| spirv-cross | vulkan-sdk-1.4.350.0 | SPIRV cross-compiler backends |
| yasio     | — | Lightweight network library |

